  <prompt>
    Register `joinIds` Handlebars helper that produces comma-separated lists suitable for FetchXML `operator='in'` clauses. Used by migrated playbooks consuming `LookupUserMembership` node output.
    Source: spec.md FR-3H1.2 (and FR-1B.2 — single implementation); AC-H1.1, AC-1B.2.
  </prompt>

  <role>Senior .NET developer (Handlebars.NET + FetchXML)</role>

  <goal>
    `{{joinIds arr}}` renders comma-separated values from `arr` (IEnumerable). Empty array → empty string. Unit tests cover: array of GUIDs, array of strings, empty array, null array.
  </goal>

  <constraints>
    <constraint source="ADR-013">AI architecture — extend existing TemplateEngine</constraint>
